extendedInfo.description: If you are Soulja Boy's fan, this app is right for you. Whenever you want to check Soulja Boy's lyrics, just open this app and choose the lyrics that you want. You don't have to access the internet to get the lyrics. We provide all Soulja Boy's lyrics here. In the Album tab, you can choose lyrics based on the album. In All lyrics tab, all of Soulja Boy's lyrics are here. You can quickly search the lyrics by using the search bar at the top of the page.Hope you guy enjoy using this app as much as I enjoy developing it. :)-------------------------------- Main Features -------------------------------- - Lyrics categorized by album - Show all lyrics - Search lyrics-------------------------------- List of albums -------------------------------- - Unsigned and Still Major Da Album Before Da Album- Souljaboytellem.com- iSouljaBoyTellem- The DeAndre Way- Promise-------------------------------- List of lyrics -------------------------------- - 30 Thousand 100 Million- Bapes- Bird Walk- Blowin' Me Kisses- Boom- Booty Got Swag- Booty Meat- Crank Dat Dance- Crank Dat Jump Rope- Crank Dat Soulja Boy- Do It Big- Donk- Don't Get Mad- Eazy- First Day Of School- Fly- Give Me A High Five- Go Head- Grammy- Gucci Bandanna- Hey Cutie- Hey You There- Hold You Down- I Got Me Some Bapes- I Love You- I Pray (Outro)- I'm Boomin'- I'm Bout Tha Stax (Intro)- I'm Winning- Kiss Me Thru The Phone- Let Me Get 'Em (ShootOut)- Look At Me- Love Money- Make My City Proud- Mean Mug- My City- Nope- Ocean Gang Splash- Pass It To Arab- Pretty Boy Swag- Real Money (Cali Life)- Report Card- Rubber Bands- She Thirsty- Shoppin' Spree- Sidekick- Snap And Roll- Soulja Boy Ain't Got No Money- Soulja Boy Tellem- Soulja Girl- Speakers Going Hammer- Steez- Stop Then Snap- Swag Daddy- Swisher Sweet Swag- Touchdown- Turn My Swag On- Whoop Rico- Wit My Yums On- Wuzhannanan- Xtra- Yahhh!- Yamaha Mama
